back at the dollar figure you feel is right?''
</P>
<P>
   Olivares leads all the starters on the staff in wins and has
thrown the club's only two complete games.
</P>
<P>
   ``I think this is a breakthrough year for him,'' Bavasi said.
``He's always been a guy that might've been cursed by his ability
to go from the bullpen to the rotation and back to the bullpen. For
