changing complexion has leaped over into the 2000 Census, which for
the first time in history will allow residents to choose more than
one race. Race experts fear the change will dilute the black
population, undermining the power that comes from sheer numbers. By
Tasha Robertson. 1000 words. 1220 words. PHOTO
