<P>
   FBN-FALCONS _ GREENVILLE, S.C. _ One of the areas that the
Falcons needed to address in the offseason was the secondary. The
team signed strong safety Marty Carter, who played last season in
Chicago, in hopes of strengthening the area. Signing with the
Falcons was a homecoming of sorts for Carter, who played high
school football in LaGrange. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 18.
