Cochrum. Brian Avery Kaye. These precious miracles all made their
Texas debuts this month to family, friends and colleagues of mine.
Never in my adult life have sfffo many people I know had babies
within days of each other. What triggered this baby boomlet in
July? According to the obstetrics staff on the maternity wings at
Arlington Memorial Hospital, blame it on El Nino. By J.R. LABBE.
