<HEADLINE>
AS CANDIDATES SPEAK, AWED HISPANICS LISTEN 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For release Sunday, Aug. 1)   (EDs: Subs byline to correct)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JAIME CASTILLO  
 c.1999 San Antonio Express-News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _ Raised in the Depression and educated a
