</P>
<P>
   SHOOT-CHRONO (Atlanta) _ A chronology of how Thursday's tragic
events unfolded, from the slaying of Mark O. Barton's wife and two
children in metro Atlanta, to the shootings in Atlanta's posh
Buckhead section to Barton's suicide north of the city. (Staff,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SHOOT-LIST (Atlanta) _ A list of those killed and wounded in
Thursday's shooting. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SHOOT-PROFILE (Atlanta) _ An in-depth profile of Mark O. Barton,
the man who apparently beat his wife and two children to death
before going on a killing spree. (Staff, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SHOOT-PSYCH (Undated) _ Talking to forensic psychologists to
find out what makes someone go on a rampage like the one in Atlanta
Thursday. (Williams, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SHOOT-DAYTRADERS (Atlanta) _ Much was made of Mark Barton's
career as a day trader. What do Atlanta day traders have to say
about it. Is the job that stressful? Are they playing with money
they don't have? What do they think about Barton's snap? (Clothier,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SHOOT-TRADERCHAT (Atlanta) _ Mining the Web chat rooms for more
discussion of mass killing among day traders and others. (Katz,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
