<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-30 19:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0328 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPOT/FEATURE-BUDGET-B     07-30 0565
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT/FEATURE-BUDGET-BOS </SLUG>
  
 For Release SATURDAY AMs, July 31, 1999  
 
