<P>
   COLOMBIA-PASTRANA (Bogota, Colombia) _ Critics and supporters
alike say time is running out for President Andres Pastrana as he
ends his first year in office. His tactics in trying to deal with
the rebels increasingly are coming under fire, and he's turning to
the United States for more money. By JOHN OTIS.
</P>
